welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Eichenau, a charming and picturesque town in Germany known for its quaint streets, beautiful parks, and warm hospitality. We invite you to immerse yourself in our culture, try our delicious local cuisine, and enjoy all that our city has to offer. We hope you have a wonderful stay!"
